        <scopecontent id="ref1">
            <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
            <p>Includes the October 27, 1951 issue of 
                <emph render="italic">Collier's Magazine</emph> which featured a full-issue hypothetical imagining of a war between the United States and the Soviet Union and an eventual United Nations occupation of the Soviet Union. Also in the collection are clippings of critical reactions to the Collier's piece from various publications including the 
                <emph render="italic">New York Times</emph> and 
                <emph render="italic">The Nation</emph>. PLEASE DIRECT FURTHER INQUIRIES TO: peter.filardo@nyu.edu</p>
        </scopecontent>
